twitch_info.title: NAFG (Not Another Falling Game) - Grinds/Playthrough - Part 1
twitch_info.description: And here begins my journey in NAFG. This game has been pretty long. Took me 37 hours 22 minutes and 14,446 deaths for the full playthrough.
